public class SimulateList

Title: Vehicle Dynamics Simulation Program

Description: vehicle dynmaics, braking system simulation

Copyright: Copyright (c) 2006 Faculty of Information Technology Engineering at Damascus University

test class for list simulation application on vehicle

Coordinate List Application:

We got a sampled linked list of coordinate values, apply it to the vehicle model in time continuous form, make it match a real world time model. For example: 100 samples, in 5 seconds, 20 sample per second, 20 transformations per second.

this is done through simulateList( ) method

set necessary data for the list application you should also provide the wheel rotational data, a list for each wheel, for now one list for them all

for now we make it simple, how ever all data should be provided, even the body positions relative to the whole vehicle when suspension is enables also data of wheel rotation arround it's vertical plane puls data for each wheel

vAngles - ArrayList angles arround three axises
wheel - ArrayList wheel rotainal angles arround it's axon

run

public void run()
a core method to apply a list of coordinates coming from outside appication or another scientific simulation, the list is time-data samples, COORDS in the list are to be simulated uniformly in DURATION time (frame-sample rate)

for now we use simple simulation, since data is not yet provided
